    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Joint statement of the Zero Emission Vehicle Transition Council
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">A joint statement from the Zero Emission Vehicle Transition Council after their first meeting to
accelerate the pace of the global transition to zero emission vehicles.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
